再答你，準備上KA去香港，已delay 4個鐘<br />\n利申MPC Gold"},{"pid":"a2f875307777e688a4f59de5dc2fe95d219106ca","tid":1117200,"uid":8253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:53:09.000Z","msg":"國泰硬件係五星航空中下游<br />\nSQ無敵 空姐個個都係好nice嘅ABC feel <br />\n利申 SQ金卡"},{"pid":"17dfc3f6a54237662d047645f4216934bc3b523d","tid":1117200,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"坐唔舒服已經死罪<br />\n我唔期待班空姐會對我依種窮毒樣笑，但係你都唔好西口西面，最仆街嘅係我講英文佢個樣就好番好多，但佢個牌寫住講粵語<br />\n野食難唔難食就好睇當地地勤，唔怪佢<br />\n<br />\n因航係香港來講係幾好，因為佢冇對手<br />\n但係上次坐完sq之後我下次去玻妹國唔會想再坐佢(如果有得揀)"},{"pid":"a30d418393e639c5eb8687efd9ebb812d72778d6","tid":1117200,"uid":47080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"空嬸、黑面空姐、舊機仲有因航雞卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不可一、不可再"},{"pid":"77595992169d937097705fb7bd78b3526d51a9c9","tid":1117200,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"咪正常航空公司一間"},{"pid":"4639ba1d3f47934bd268b3a175f99afe49aabb3c","tid":1117200,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77595992169d937097705fb7bd78b3526d51a9c9","tid":1117200,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"咪正常航空公司一間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"睇下大家對佢觀感係點者"},{"pid":"eceb54fc92a5b8f0dc4baad03f0d2ed41959e3c4","tid":1117200,"uid":2319,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"香港出國首選cx <br />\n航班時間大部分都靚<br />\n東南亞唔駛講啦<br />\n而家連歐洲long haul 都好左port<br />\n時間都幾好 零晨上機去到朝早<br />\nFlight attendants 就唔多覺有西面<br />\n飛機餐就普普通通啦<br />\n唯一要屌既就係好多舊機都唔好坐<br />\n要坐cx盡量都揀a350坐"},{"pid":"ceb71bf9e3cc3924f2e8b153701168defb205185","tid":1117200,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4639ba1d3f47934bd268b3a175f99afe49aabb3c","tid":1117200,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid